msgctxt "44_Okudera"
msgid ""
"Saejima, we shouldn't go any further than this. We don't want to run into "
"Yama-oroshi."
msgstr ""
"Saejima, non dovremmo spingerci oltre. Non vogliamo imbatterci nello Yama-"
"oroshi."

msgctxt "56_Saejima"
msgid "Okay. Got it."
msgstr "Okay. Capito."
